Description: Chimaera distributed runtime system
 Chimaera is a distributed runtime system for high-performance I/O operations.
 It provides a modular framework for creating custom I/O modules (ChiMods)
 and orchestrating distributed task execution.
 .
 This package includes:
  - Core Chimaera runtime libraries
  - Admin module for runtime management
  - BDev module for block device operations
  - Runtime executables (chimaera_start_runtime, chimaera_stop_runtime)
  - Development headers and CMake configuration files
